library(Seurat)
library(NeuronChat)
library(PRROC)
Adult.Ex <- readRDS('../rds/4.Adult.Ex.rds')
Adult.Ex.barcode <- readRDS('../rds/5.Adult.Ex.barcode.rds')

1 

data(list='cortex_data')

2 

# sender matrix
df_sender <- as.data.frame(t(Adult.Ex.barcode@assays$RNA@data[LT_gene,]))
df_sender[,'Cluster'] <- as.character(Adult.Ex.barcode$Ex_subtype)
df_sender[match(colnames(Adult.IT.barcode),rownames(df_sender)),'Cluster'] <- as.character(Adult.IT.barcode$IT_Subtype)
rownames(df_sender) <- paste('sender_',rownames(df_sender),sep='')
# receiver matrix
df_receiver <- as.data.frame(t(Adult.Ex.barcode@assays$RNA@data[LT_gene,]))
df_receiver[,'Cluster'] <- paste('Proj_', Adult.Ex.barcode$Proj_module, sep='')
rownames(df_receiver) <- paste('receiver_', rownames(df_receiver), sep='')
# merge
df_merge <- rbind(df_sender[,-ncol(df_sender)], df_receiver[,-ncol(df_receiver)])
sender.names <- c("L2/3a IT Dorsal","L2/3a IT Ventral","L2/3b IT Dorsal","L2/3b IT Ventral","L5 IT Dorsal","L5 IT Ventral","L6 IT Dorsal","L6 IT Ventral","PT")
receiver.names <- c("Proj_PT","Proj_ITi-D","Proj_ITi-V","Proj_ITc")

neu <- createNeuronChat(t(as.matrix(df_merge)),
                        DB='mouse',
                        group.by = c(df_sender$Cluster, df_receiver$Cluster),
                        )
neu <- run_NeuronChat(neu,
                      sender=sender.names, receiver=receiver.names,
                      M=100)
neu_aggregated <- net_aggregation(neu@net, method='weight')
colnames(neu_aggregated) <- c('M-PT','M-ITi-D','M-ITi-V','M-ITc')

observed projection

obs_aggregated <- matrix(nrow = nrow(neu_aggregated), ncol = ncol(neu_aggregated))
rownames(obs_aggregated) <- rownames(neu_aggregated)
colnames(obs_aggregated) <- colnames(neu_aggregated)
for (i in 1:nrow(obs_aggregated)){
  for (j in 1:ncol(obs_aggregated)){
    obs_aggregated[i,j] <- mean(Adult.Ex.barcode@meta.data[which(df_sender$Cluster == rownames(obs_aggregated)[i]), colnames(obs_aggregated)[j]], na.rm=T)
  }
}
#df_predicted <- t(apply(neu_aggregated, 1, function(x){x/max(x)}))
#df_observed <- t(apply(obs_aggregated, 1, function(x){x/max(x)}))
df_predicted <- neu_aggregated/max(neu_aggregated)
df_observed <- obs_aggregated/max(obs_aggregated)
df_plot <- df_observed
df_plot[which(df_plot<0.5)] <- 0
netVisual_circle_neuron(df_plot, vertex.label.cex = 1, arrow.size=0)

df_plot <- df_predicted
df_plot[which(df_plot<0.5)] <- 0
netVisual_circle_neuron(df_plot, vertex.label.cex = 1, arrow.size=0)

PRROC_obj <- roc.curve(scores.class0=df_predicted,weights.class0=df_observed,curve=TRUE)
par(mar = c(5, 5, 4, 1),cex.lab=1.5, cex.axis=1.5,cex.main=1.5)
plot(PRROC_obj,xlab = 'False positive rate')

3 

# sender matrix
df_sender <- as.data.frame(t(Adult.Ex.barcode@assays$RNA@data[LT_gene,]))
df_sender[,'Cluster'] <- as.character(Adult.Ex.barcode$Ex_subtype)
df_sender[match(colnames(Adult.IT.barcode),rownames(df_sender)),'Cluster'] <- as.character(Adult.IT.barcode$IT_Subtype)
rownames(df_sender) <- paste('sender_',rownames(df_sender),sep='')
# receiver matrix
df_receiver <- as.data.frame(t(Adult.Ex.barcode@assays$RNA@data[LT_gene,]))
df_receiver[,'Cluster'] <- Adult.Ex.barcode$Proj_cluster
rownames(df_receiver) <- paste('receiver_', rownames(df_receiver), sep='')
# merge
df_merge <- rbind(df_sender[,-ncol(df_sender)], df_receiver[,-ncol(df_receiver)])
ITi_D <- c("VIS-I","CP-I","CP-I + CP-C","CP-I + RSP-I","CP-I + AUD-I", "SSp-I", "AUD-I", "RSP-I", "RSP-I + ACB-I")
ITc <- c("PL-C", "CP-I + PL-C", "PL-C + CP-C", "CP-C", "CP-C + ACB-I","ACB-C", "ECT-C", "AId-C")
PT <- c("LHA-I", "DR", "VTA-I")
ITi_V <- c("ECT-I", "BLA-I","BLA-I + ACB-I", "ACB-I + AId-I","ACB-I + PL-C","ACB-I + CP-I","ACB-I","AId-I + CP-I","AId-I")

sender.names <- c("L2/3a IT Dorsal","L2/3a IT Ventral","L2/3b IT Dorsal","L2/3b IT Ventral","L5 IT Dorsal","L5 IT Ventral","L6 IT Dorsal","L6 IT Ventral","PT")
receiver.names <- c(PT,ITi_D,ITi_V,ITc)

neu <- createNeuronChat(t(as.matrix(df_merge)),
                        DB='mouse',
                        group.by = c(df_sender$Cluster, df_receiver$Cluster),
                        )
neu <- run_NeuronChat(neu,
                      sender=sender.names, receiver=receiver.names,
                      M=10)
neu_aggregated <- net_aggregation(neu@net, method='weight')
#colnames(neu_aggregated) <- c('M-PT','M-ITi-D','M-ITi-V','M-ITc')

observed projection

obs_aggregated <- matrix(nrow = nrow(neu_aggregated), ncol = ncol(neu_aggregated))
rownames(obs_aggregated) <- rownames(neu_aggregated)
colnames(obs_aggregated) <- colnames(neu_aggregated)
for (i in 1:nrow(obs_aggregated)){
  for (j in 1:ncol(obs_aggregated)){
    BC <- strsplit(colnames(obs_aggregated)[j], split = ' + ', fixed = T)[[1]]
    obs_aggregated[i,j] <- mean(as.matrix(Adult.Ex.barcode@meta.data[which(df_sender$Cluster == rownames(obs_aggregated)[i]), BC]), na.rm=T)
  }
}
df_predicted <- t(apply(neu_aggregated, 1, function(x){x/max(x)}))
df_observed <- t(apply(obs_aggregated, 1, function(x){x/max(x)}))
PRROC_obj <- roc.curve(scores.class0=df_predicted,weights.class0=df_observed,curve=TRUE)
par(mar = c(5, 5, 4, 1),cex.lab=1.5, cex.axis=1.5,cex.main=1.5)
plot(PRROC_obj,xlab = 'False positive rate')

df_plot <- df_predicted
df_plot[which(df_plot<0.5)] <- 0
netVisual_circle_neuron(df_plot, vertex.label.cex = 1, arrow.size=0)

df_plot <- df_observed
df_plot[which(df_plot<0.5)] <- 0
netVisual_circle_neuron(df_plot, vertex.label.cex = 1, arrow.size=0)
